@page "/"

<PageTitle>SubTrack — Akilli Abonelik Yonetimi</PageTitle>

<section class="flex-1 flex items-center px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full">
        <div class="h-1.5 w-16 bg-primary mb-8 rounded-full"></div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-primary-dark leading-tight tracking-tight">
            SubTrack
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Streaming, muzik, verimlilik ve oyun aboneliklerinizi tek bir panelden takip edin.
            Otomatik yenileme uyarilari ve kullanilmayan abonelik tespiti ile aylik harcamanizi gorunur kilin.
            MBP 206 ders projesi olarak gelistirilen, tamamen acik kaynak bir platform.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
            <a href="/login" class="btn-primary">
                Giris Yap
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/ilkerefeipek/mbp206-SubTrack" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
               class="inline-flex items-center text-slate-600 hover:text-primary-dark font-medium transition">
                GitHub'da incele
                <span class="ml-2" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <dl class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10">
            <div>
                <dt class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-dark">6</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">veri modeli</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
                <dt class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-dark">5</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">kategori</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
                <dt class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-dark">7</dt>
                <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">demo abonelik</dd>
            </div>
        </dl>
    </div>
</section>

<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 px-6 py-6">
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        MBP 206 — Izmir Ekonomi Universitesi
        <span class="mx-2 text-slate-300">|</span>
        Grup 2.2
    </p>
</footer>
